{
  "stem": "12289.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- but that-- that exam was-- was, sort of, more or less compulsory, to have that exam, to enter the Foreign Service at that time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and that-- that helped me to-- to be-- being accepted by-- by the Foreign Office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then I was sent to Berlin, where I was working with-- that was in 1940, when I was working with trade, the trade relations between Sweden and-- and Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we had a substantial-- a substantial exchange of-- of-- of goods and change that we-- we delivered, which we have been criticized, of course, very much for that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We delivered the iron ore and all that to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we received coal and all that for heating our houses and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was a big, big exchange of-- of-- of trade exchange, at that time, very important for the-- for our survival, so to say.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we traded-- we traded, also, of course, with the other side, with the-- the Allies and-- and negotiated with them, also.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- but I happened to come on-- on the sort of German desk, on the German side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on a-- on-- of course, on a very low level, I was dealing with these problems in-- at the embassy in Berlin, at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then after that, I was transferred home, for a short while, while I was-- when I was dealing with the Hungarian, the Hungarian trade relations, which led to my-- me being transferred to Budapest in 1942.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, we had to have-- maintain a kind of correct-- even if you didn't like the system and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
